\npart of $\\phi$ near $\\mathcal{I}^-$. Similar results are obtained for\npolynomially decaying timelike boundary data. The paper uses methods developed\nby Angelopoulos--Aretakis--Gajic and is essentially self-contained.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 May 2021 18:00:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 9 Jul 2021 15:50:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-12"}
