entify it with the enhancement $Y(4008)$\nobserved by the Belle Collaboration. A detailed analysis reveals that different\nmechanism is responsible for the creation of $Y(4008)$. Hence, the bump\nassociated with $Y(4008)$ should not be interpreted as an independent\nresonance, but rather as a manifestation of the strong coupling of $\\psi(4040)$\nto the $D^*D$ channel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 May 2021 14:41:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-19"}
